WEBVTT


00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:01.200
Hello, ma'am.

00:00:01.201 --> 00:00:03.281
I'm sorry to do this here at work for you,

00:00:03.282 --> 00:00:04.961
but I'm here to inform you

00:00:04.962 --> 00:00:07.121
that you have been let go of your position as a teacher

00:00:07.122 --> 00:00:10.381
here at the school, and you are also under arrest.

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:13.140
What? Why?

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:15.760
Well, you are considered a threat to children,

00:00:15.761 --> 00:00:18.881
and you have exposed all of these children in your class

00:00:18.882 --> 00:00:21.281
to pornography. What?

00:00:21.282 --> 00:00:25.481
I have never done that. I can see where the confusion has come from,

00:00:25.482 --> 00:00:29.501
but as you know, we do have new laws that have just been passed,

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:34.020
and these new laws now categorize all LGBTQ relationships

00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:38.260
as pornographic. And if you expose children to those relationships,

00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:41.800
you are exposing children to pornography. What?

00:00:41.801 --> 00:00:43.801
I just have a photo of us at my desk,

00:00:43.802 --> 00:00:45.721
and honestly, we look like we're friends.

00:00:45.722 --> 00:00:48.461
We're not doing anything romantic in that photo.

00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:50.520
If this was a week ago, then, yes,

00:00:50.521 --> 00:00:52.161
you would be right. However,

00:00:52.162 --> 00:00:55.101
the new laws do state that it is inappropriate.

00:00:55.320 --> 00:00:59.160
Children are only allowed to know that men and women can be together,

00:00:59.161 --> 00:01:00.921
nothing else. Okay,

00:01:00.922 --> 00:01:03.081
well, I'll take the photo down, then.

00:01:03.082 --> 00:01:03.961
I'm sorry, ma'am,

00:01:03.962 --> 00:01:05.401
but the damage has already been done.

00:01:05.402 --> 00:01:06.921
The kids have already seen the photo.

00:01:06.922 --> 00:01:09.521
And plus, let's not even get started on your social media.

00:01:09.522 --> 00:01:11.781
It's all over all of your social medias

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:14.880
that you are supposedly a lesbian.

00:01:14.881 --> 00:01:15.741
And,

00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:17.440
yeah, we just.

00:01:17.441 --> 00:01:19.161
That's also very inappropriate.

00:01:19.162 --> 00:01:21.121
Children cannot see that. So

00:01:21.122 --> 00:01:22.561
I am sorry to say that you

00:01:22.562 --> 00:01:25.701
Are under arrest for sex crimes against children.

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:29.220
This is ridiculous. I'm just living my life and existing.

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:31.240
And not to alarm you or anything,

00:01:31.241 --> 00:01:32.861
but here in the state of Florida,

00:01:33.080 --> 00:01:37.940
sex crimes against children do carry a maximum penalty of death.

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:41.100
This is absurd. I haven't hurt anybody.

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:43.264
Sorry, ma'am. That's just how it is.
